466
00:33:23,084 --> 00:33:25,253
Mas Tammy Thompson é menina.

467
00:33:27,046 --> 00:33:27,880
Steve.

468
00:33:28,673 --> 00:33:29,507
Sim?

469
00:33:38,433 --> 00:33:41,060
-Puta merda.
-É.

470
00:33:42,145 --> 00:33:42,979
Puta merda.

471
00:33:54,991 --> 00:33:55,825
Steve...

472
00:33:57,076 --> 00:33:58,202
morreu de overdose?

473
00:33:59,078 --> 00:34:00,163
Não, eu...

474
00:34:01,873 --> 00:34:03,416
-só estou pensando.
-Certo.

475
00:34:06,127 --> 00:34:07,045
Tipo...

476
00:34:09,005 --> 00:34:11,340
a Tammy Thompson é bonita e tal, mas...

477
00:34:13,092 --> 00:34:15,344
