Traidor.

568
00:41:52,843 --> 00:41:55,638
Ai, não. Meu Deus. Vamos.

569
00:42:00,184 --> 00:42:01,101
Devagar.

570
00:42:04,688 --> 00:42:05,856
Fique pressionando.

571
00:42:06,857 --> 00:42:08,984
Vou buscar ajuda. Vou chamar alguém.

572
00:42:23,624 --> 00:42:26,544
Jim!

573
00:42:27,169 --> 00:42:28,671
Pegaram o Alexey, Jim!

574
00:42:29,588 --> 00:42:32,716
