Malditas salsichas.

597
00:44:43,722 --> 00:44:45,182
Meu Deus.

598
00:44:47,434 --> 00:44:48,602
Ai, não.

599
00:45:30,728 --> 00:45:35,649
Vasilev, está aí? Vasilev, responda!

600
00:45:53,709 --> 00:45:54,543
O que foi?

601
00:45:57,713 --> 00:45:58,547
Ei!

602
00:45:59,131 --> 00:46:01,008
-Larry.
-Joyce.

603
00:46:08,098 --> 00:46:09,224
Isso, moça!

604
00:46:57,523 --> 00:46:58,482
Oi!

605
00:47:16,124 --> 00:47:17,125
Camarada.

606
00:47:17,668 --> 00:47:18,502
Me solte.

607
00:47:27,845 --> 00:47:31,014
Caralho, filho da puta!

608
00:47:37,271 --> 00:47:38,188
Ei!

609
00:47:40,399 --> 00:47:42,943
Pise fundo! Vamos!

610
00:47:45,654 --> 00:47:46,780
Alexey?

611
00:47:53,036 --> 00:47:54,454
...no primeiro piso.

612
00:47:54,955 --> 00:47:56,748
Ei, traduza.

613
00:47:57,332 --> 00:47:59,251
Repito, encontramos as crianças.

614
00:47:59,668 --> 00:48:02,170
Ainda estão no shopping. Primeiro piso.

