645
00:51:08,982 --> 00:51:10,984
On!

646
00:51:11,068 --> 00:51:12,611
-O que houve?
-O que foi?

647
00:51:12,861 --> 00:51:15,113
-Minha perna.
-A perna dela. Certo...

648
00:51:16,448 --> 00:51:17,449
